== Spanish ==
=== Etymology ===
''[[coño]]'' + ''-azo'', "giant [[cunt]]"

=== Noun ===
'''coñazo''' (''vulgar'')
# (''Spain'') An extreme annoyance.
#: ''¡Qué coñazo!'' "How extremely annoying!", lit. "what a giant cunt!"

